data.text: Ok wan, ok wan, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
Ang ºo momiyo ogendini penjo niya,
To nyisechegi mopa gin fedha gi dhahabu,
Gin gi dhogi, to kata kamano ok ginyal wuoyo,
Gin gi it, to ok ginyal winjo wach,
Gin gi lwetegi, to ok ginyal mulo,
Yaye dhood jo-Israel, genuru kuom Jehova Nyasaye,
Yaye dhood joka Harun, genuru kuom Jehova Nyasaye,
Un joma omiyo Jehova Nyasaye luor, keturu genou kuome,
Jehova Nyasaye parowa kendo obiro gwedhowa;
obiro gwedho joma oluoro Jehova Nyasaye,
Mad iyud gweth moa kuom Jehova Nyasaye,
Polo malo mogik en mar Jehova Nyasaye,
Joma osetho ok ema pak Jehova Nyasaye,
en wan ema wadendo Jehova Nyasaye
